      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-stp-tip-sel    to   r-fix-tip-sel          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice stampante                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-stp-cod-stp    to   r-fix-cod-stp          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo di stampa                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
